{"tid":1971136,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"恥笑失業廢老梁振英  劉夢熊：「日日數《蘋果日報》好無聊，廢人一個」","createTime":"2020-04-13T16:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T12:51:46.000Z","uid":2054,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"29bd661a46b0bb311690acdb74e275998564344e","tid":1971136,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T16:34:41.000Z","msg":"睇全文專訪請訂閱蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200414&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=60826921\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200414%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D60826921&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B86mkGRIJ7ARjMQoHd6uTSg0%3D&h=19ce975b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200414%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D60826921&h=1caaba9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200414&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=60826921</a><br />\n<br />\n至於在他心中恩將仇報、分裂香港人的梁振英又是甚麼股票？劉夢熊說得更狠，「一隻停牌股，冇資產，冇新業務注入，已經交易所勒令停牌，等緊取消上市地位。」現時本港有不少長期停牌未能說服聯交所發證監會准許復牌，原因不外乎是未能刊出財務報表（沒有政績）、財務出現問題（誠信有問題）、資產不足（能力低）、股東爭拗（撕裂社會）、公眾持股量低（專制、民意極低）。<br />\n<br />\n他形容有多項因素令梁振英這隻停牌股沒有希望，「UGL事件仲俾人追擊緊，冇得連任亦反映中央不信任，日日數《蘋果日報》好無聊，廢人一個，一定係18個月之內執骨嘅股票。」他又以一對活寶貝來形容林鄭及梁振英，「特點係唔可以由上環行到中環，一定俾人鬧死。」"},{"pid":"432d1d5b92728192f45602065795054c14f57c8b","tid":1971136,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T16:36:10.000Z","msg":"食少一餐訂蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ccdb1779ee18d79bc26635d5d15593c29a7f74","tid":1971136,"uid":269061,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T16:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WtFXitr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWtFXitr.jpg&h=1edec668&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1633cef95cc52089d4b60493ef92c9fbc80772da","tid":1971136,"uid":258377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":